{"type":"answer","id":49816,"parentType":"question","parentId":8260,"uid":1927,"contents":"百度百科：<br>\n调制对比度<br>\n调制对比度又称<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/contrast%20modulation/19824656\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">contrast modulation</a>，简称为CM。CM的中文名为“<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%98%8E%E6%9A%97%E8%B0%83%E5%88%B6%E6%AF%94/19863384\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">明暗调制比</a>”、“<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%AE%E5%BA%A6%E8%B0%83%E5%88%B6%E6%AF%94\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">亮度调制比</a>”、“调制对比度” 。<br>\n<br>\n<ul><br>\n<li>中文名<br>\n调制对比度</li><br>\n<li>外文名<br>\ncontrast modulation</li><br>\n<li>缩写<br>\nCM</li><br>\n</ul><br>\n调制对比度是相间黑白线的亮度变化值。<br>\n产出公式和测定模式如下：<br>\n　　产出公式 (Michelson Contrast) : Cm = (LW-LB)/(LW+LB), LW : White 的亮度, LB : Black的亮度<br>\n　　测定模式 (Black &amp; White Grille)<br>\n<center><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/javascript:;\"><a href=\"https://imgsrc.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/bd3eb13533fa828b86ce2096f51f4134960a5ad1.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgsrc.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/bd3eb13533fa828b86ce2096f51f4134960a5ad1.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgsrc.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/bd3eb13533fa828b86ce2096f51f4134960a5ad1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></a></center><br>\nCm（<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Contrast%20modulation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Contrast modulation</a>） 是判断是否达到指定分辨率的基准，达到50%以上即可判定达到指定分辨率。该指数与画质或鲜明度无关。","date":"2019-09-10","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":1}